data.description: Willow Glen neighborhood with walking distance to Sanger High. Endless possibilities in this spacious home to entertain and enjoy! Spacious Primary suite with two closets of which one is a large walk in, double sinks, separate jetted tub and shower. Kitchen is for the chef including a gas stove, pantry and large center island. Three more bedrooms upstairs, bathroom along with the utility room. A separate loft upstairs that could be a work area, game area or family entertainment space. Bath downstairs next to a room that could be used as a bedroom. Formal Dining and Living Room however you want to use. Did I mention a three car garage with a large driveway for additional cars. The Primary suite has french doors and a deck overlooking the backyard. Perfect to have your own private view of the fireworks at Sanger HIgh on the 4th of July. Nice patio with extra cement in the backyard to put in an outdoor Kitchen. Solar to help with utility bills. Close to shopping, schools, a park area close by and Jensen Ave. In the City and close to the Country. So much to see in this wonderful home to make it your own.
